00:31:36,937 --> 00:31:38,690
Is that why you sat him next to you?

478
00:31:38,773 --> 00:31:41,735
Bob, as you said,
the Republicans control Congress.

479
00:31:48,867 --> 00:31:50,326
Any luck with Birch?

480
00:31:51,369 --> 00:31:54,038
No list yet.
I'll keep working him.

481
00:31:54,121 --> 00:31:56,290
Where's Dr. Cooke?

